name: JsModule
signature: @Target([AnnotationTarget.CLASS, AnnotationTarget.PROPERTY, AnnotationTarget.FUNCTION, AnnotationTarget.FILE]) annotation class JsModule

items.desc: Denotes an external declaration that must be imported from native JavaScript library.
name of a module to import declaration from. It is not interpreted by the Kotlin compiler, it's passed as is directly to the target module system.
